oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Will The Circuit Be Unbroken - Johnny Trash recording - 1974 - WETE
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Recording of Will The Circuit Be Unbroken (Brighter Days), as performed by Johnny Trash (performer), in 1974 on radio station WETE (Knoxville, Tenn.) Recording also contains WETE stations I. D., news, and weather reports.
